Quickstrike:




Quickstrike jumped from the optics lasers. His ridged metal feet 
caught him from slipping or loosing his balance, but what hit him 
threw him to the ground on his back. He wanted to get immediately up 
and continue the fight, but something was wrong. There was a terrible 
pain at his head that restricted him from functioning right. He 
slumped down on the floor, struggling to get up.
